title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Mar 10 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Mar 10 2022
description:
Infuriating! Biden extends mask mandate on planes. Clay says he rarely comes into the show angry, but this did it. Buck thinks it's done to purposely humiliate. Record-high inflation now blamed on Putin. Senator Ron Johnson joins Clay and Buck to outline the numerous ways the Biden Administration has weakened America. Psaki blames gas prices, inflation on Putin.
